    public class ViewHabitActivity
extends android.support.v7.app.AppCompatActivity
implements EditHabitDialog.EditHabitDialogListener
    Created by Andrew on 11/6/2017. This activity allows the user to view the details of a specific habit. The user can also edit or delete the habit in this activity, as well as add habit events.
